      • AbstractCommand

        public AbstractCommand(java.lang.String name,
                       java.lang.String description,
                       java.lang.String usage,
                       int minArgs,
                       int maxArgs,
                       java.lang.String... keywords)
        Creates a new command.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the command.
        description - What the command does.
        usage - How to use this command (eg. /giveitem <id> <amt> <player>)
        minArgs - The minimum arguments that must be passed without causing an error message (usage message). Use -1 to disable.
        maxArgs - The maximum arguments that must be passed without causing an error message (usage message). Use -1 to disable.
        keywords - the keywords of this command.
